\"She told the PA news agency: \\\"I probably should not have run on the day I gave birth.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the PA news agency\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I actually pulled my calf on a run in the morning and then gave birth that evening.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1152, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my calf\", \"from\": 1087, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"a run\", \"from\": 1098, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1118}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1138}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, I was heavily over my usual running weight and obviously my gait was completely different because I had a big belly.\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my usual running weight\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"my gait\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"a big belly\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1284}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe if I had not pulled my calf I'd have said it was fine.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my calf\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But yeah, looking back, with two weeks to go, I probably could have just chilled out a little bit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two weeks\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth, determined to hit the ground running once Frederick was born, found medical research into training while pregnant to be limited.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 1503, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.690326267646597e-18, \"text\": \"Frederick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_the_Great\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"medical research\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1545}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Until the turn of the century, it was rare to see women return to the top of their sport after giving birth.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the turn\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"the century\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth is grateful to the doctors and sports scientists at the National Sports Centre at Bisham Abbey and British Triathlon for their support.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}, {\"begin\": 1767, \"end\": 1789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\", \"score\": 0.582006492548568, \"rank\": 0.718193879668866, \"text\": \"National Sports Centre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lilleshall_Hall\"}, {\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Triathlon_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the doctors\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"sports scientists\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1759}, {\"ngram\": \"Bisham Abbey\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"their support\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were certain things I obviously did follow,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"certain things\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The massive one is not running for 12 weeks post-birth.\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The massive one\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"12 weeks\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"post\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you come back too early, you can have problems later down the line.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I followed all the advice, but it was the stuff they were not sure on that I kind of explored myself.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the advice\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"the stuff\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was still lifting heavy weights in the gym.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"heavy weights\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the gym\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I took the information and filtered it for me.\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the information\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They helped me find my own boundaries and explore what I could and could not manage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own boundaries\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth stressed that throughout her pregnancy she never allowed her heart rate to go beyond 150 beats per minute, while her approach, so far, appears to be paying off.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her pregnancy\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"her heart rate\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"150 beats\", \"from\": 2417, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"minute\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"her approach\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Running aside, she is closing in on the performance levels that saw her win Olympic gold and finish second overall in the 2019 World Series after multiple podium finishes.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the performance levels\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2019 World Series\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple podium finishes\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not far away,\\\" said the 2017 European champion.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999996392508106, \"rank\": 3.0812784402671664e-07, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just not as good as I was before, yet.\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been big changes in my life, having Fred and not training as much.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big changes\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"Fred\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's interesting to see how my body will react to doing less training and more recovery.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my body\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"less training\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"more recovery\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It could go either way.\\\"\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2959, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Learmonth has been surprised by her progress as she targets the first Indoor World Cup event of the season in Lievin, France, for her return to competitive action at the end of March.\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 3144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2961, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jess_Learmonth\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9273489353929126e-29, \"text\": \"Learmonth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", 